    <title>Bass Loudness</title>
    <p>The ear is less sensitive to low frequencies when listening at low volume. This plugin developed by MDA allows the bass level to be adjusted measuring the "equal-loudness contour".</p>
    <terms>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Loudness</em>
            </title>
            <p>Source level relative to listening level (based on a 100 dB SPL maximum level).</p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Output</em>
            </title>
            <p>Change output level.</p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Link</em>
            </title>
            <p>Automatically adjusts Output to maintain a consistent tonal balance at all levels.</p>
        </item>
    </terms>
